data.text:
W S B R Letter Values in Word Scrabble and Words With Friends

Here are the values for the letters W S B R in two of the most popular word scramble games.

Scrabble

The letters WSBR are worth 9 points in Scrabble

W 4

S 1

B 3

R 1

Words With Friends

The letters WSBR are worth 10 points in Words With Friends

W 4

S 1

B 4

R 1

Scrambling the Letters in WSBR

According to our other word scramble maker, WSBR can be scrambled in many ways. The different ways a word can be scrambled is called "permutations" of the word.

According to Google, this is the definition of permutation:

a way, especially one of several possible variations, in which a set or number of things can be ordered or arranged.

How is this helpful? Well, it shows you the anagrams of wsbr scrambled in different ways and helps you recognize the set of letters more easily. It will help you the next time these letters, W S B R come up in a word scramble game.

BWSR WBSR BSWR SWBR SBWR

We stopped it at 5, but there are so many ways to scramble WSBR!
